      <title>加密行业加大对沃伦反犯罪法案的攻击力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/crypto-industry-steps-up-attacks-on-senator-elizabeth-warren-s-anti-crime-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币行业正在加大对参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦(Elizabeth Warren)反犯罪立法的攻击，认为该立法的通过将有效地扼杀美国的该行业。]]></description>
