    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦保守派政党组建联盟，挫败汗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/bhutto-s-party-joins-sharif-s-coalition-seeking-to-run-pakistan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦的两个保守派政党同意组建政府，此举打破了近两周的僵局，并可能使被监禁的前总理伊姆兰·汗所在的政党远离政府，尽管该党在该国有争议的选举中赢得了最多席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/bhutto-s-party-joins-sharif-s-coalition-seeking-to-run-pakistan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 19:19:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特考虑刺激养老金投资英国资产的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/jeremy-hunt-weighs-plans-to-spur-pension-funds-to-invest-in-uk-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特正在考虑刺激养老基金增加对英国资产投资的计划，这是政府提振经济增长和帮助陷入困境的英国股市的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/jeremy-hunt-weighs-plans-to-spur-pension-funds-to-invest-in-uk-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 17:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
